### Budget Allocator CLI
A simple command-line tool to manage departmental budgets, built in Rust using clap, with JSON-based data persistence and CSV export functionality.

## Features
1. Add budget categories
2. View all budgets
3. Edit amounts or names
4. Remove budget categories
5. Export budgets to a .csv file
6. Data is automatically saved in budgets.json

```bash
cargo run -- add IT 3000
cargo run -- view
cargo run -- edit-amount IT 5000
cargo run -- edit-name IT Tech
cargo run -- remove Tech
cargo run -- export-csv
```
